# 🔥 Prim vs Kruskal

| Feature         | Prim           | Kruskal       |
| --------------- | -------------- | ------------- |
| Approach        | Vertex Based   | Edge Based    |
| Uses            | Priority Queue | Sorting + DSU |
| Best For        | Dense Graphs   | Sparse Graphs |
| Time Complexity | O(E log V)     | O(E log E)    |

